  "chapterIndex": 2,
  "title": "Preparing to Teach",
  "originalHtml": "<p data-key=\"188\"><span data-key=\"189\"><span data-offset-key=\"189:0\"><span data-slate-zero-width=\"n\">​</span></span></span></p><p data-key=\"190\"><span data-key=\"191\"><span data-offset-key=\"191:0\"><strong>Let's get ready to teach this lesson sequence!</strong></span><span data-offset-key=\"191:1\"> </span></span></p><div data-key=\"192\" class=\"BlockWrapper__block--U1QBoci undefined\"><div class=\"BlockImage__component--np2T9it\" data-alignment=\"center\"><figure class=\"BlockImage__figure--trN7ey9\"><img class=\"BlockImage__image--Oer5P08\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/com.appolearning.files/production/uploads/uploaded_file/2b146bb1-7092-4504-a3f2-bf1dfac4dfd9/marten-bjork-rH8O0FHFpfw-unsplash.jpg\"><figcaption class=\"BlockCaption__normal--LwbSyCy\" data-readonly=\"true\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\"><div class=\"Flow__vertical--MIpOnl5 Flow__standard--zZPuF1Y\"><ul data-key=\"193\"><li data-key=\"194\"><p data-key=\"195\"><span data-key=\"196\"><span data-offset-key=\"196:0\"><span data-slate-zero-width=\"n\">​</span></span></span></p></li></ul><p data-key=\"197\"><span data-key=\"198\"><span data-offset-key=\"198:0\">Photo by Marten Bjork on Unsplash</span></span></p></div></figcaption></figure></div></div><div data-key=\"199\" class=\"BlockWrapper__block--U1QBoci undefined\"><div class=\"BlockHeader__component--Pa9vmaO\"><h2><span data-key=\"200\"><span data-offset-key=\"200:0\">Choose a Text Set</span></span></h2></div></div><p data-key=\"201\"><span data-key=\"202\"><span data-offset-key=\"202:0\"><strong>The Ranking Evidence lesson sequence features five text set options.</strong></span><span data-offset-key=\"202:1\"> The first step in preparing to teach the lesson sequence is to select the text set you will use with your students. </span></span></p><p data-key=\"203\"><span data-key=\"204\"><span data-offset-key=\"204:0\">Consider the following questions as a guide for your decision:</span></span></p><ul data-key=\"205\"><li data-key=\"206\"><p data-key=\"207\"><span data-key=\"208\"><span data-offset-key=\"208:0\">Which topics will be most interesting to your students?</span></span></p></li><li data-key=\"209\"><p data-key=\"210\"><span data-key=\"211\"><span data-offset-key=\"211:0\">Which text set provides opportunities that best meet the needs of your learners?</span></span></p></li><li data-key=\"212\"><p data-key=\"213\"><span data-key=\"214\"><span data-offset-key=\"214:0\">Which text sets are more accessible to your learners?</span></span></p></li></ul><p data-key=\"215\"><span data-key=\"216\"><span data-offset-key=\"216:0\">To get started, take some time to explore the full text set in each option below. You don't necessarily need to do a close reading of every single text in each text set option at this point, but it would be helpful to open and preview each text to get a sense of the format, length, vocabulary, level of complexity, etc.  </span></span></p><p data-key=\"217\"><span data-key=\"218\"><span data-offset-key=\"218:0\"><strong>One other note to consider as you are choosing a topic.</strong></span><span data-offset-key=\"218:1\"> Sometimes teachers feel like they need to avoid selecting text set topics that their students are unfamiliar with. However, in NWP's experience with text sets in the College, Career, and Community Writer's Program (C3WP), teachers often found that the text set topics their students didn't know much (or anything about) provided the highest engagement. So, keep that in mind when you are thinking about which topic you might choose. </span></span></p><div data-slate-void=\"true\" data-key=\"219\"><div><div data-key=\"219\" class=\"BlockWrapper__block--U1QBoci undefined\"><div><iframe src=\"https://www.canva.com/design/DAFSDtfcPfw/qPOls4YDUzeB-e1nZNFrhQ/view?embed\" height=\"1500\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-forms allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\" style=\"border-radius: 10px; width: 100%;\"></iframe></div></div></div></div><div data-key=\"222\" class=\"BlockWrapper__block--U1QBoci undefined\"><div class=\"BlockHeader__component--Pa9vmaO\"><h2><span data-key=\"223\"><span data-offset-key=\"223:0\">Close Reading of Lesson Sequence </span></span></h2></div></div><p data-key=\"224\"><span data-key=\"225\"><span data-offset-key=\"225:0\"><strong>In preparation for teaching</strong></span><span data-offset-key=\"225:1\">, take some time to do a close reading of the</span><span data-offset-key=\"225:2\"><strong> </strong></span><span data-offset-key=\"225:3\">Ranking Evidence Lesson Sequence for the text set you selected. </span></span></p><p data-key=\"226\"><span data-key=\"227\"><span data-offset-key=\"227:0\">As you read the lesson sequence, make note of\r</span></span></p><ul data-key=\"228\"><li data-key=\"229\"><p data-key=\"230\"><span data-key=\"231\"><span data-offset-key=\"231:0\">Number of suggested days and overall pacing</span></span></p></li><li data-key=\"232\"><p data-key=\"233\"><span data-key=\"234\"><span data-offset-key=\"234:0\">Resources and handouts to prepare\r</span></span></p></li><li data-key=\"235\"><p data-key=\"236\"><span data-key=\"237\"><span data-offset-key=\"237:0\">Student skills/conceptual understandings\r</span></span></p></li><li data-key=\"238\"><p data-key=\"239\"><span data-key=\"240\"><span data-offset-key=\"240:0\">Connections to your curriculum and/or \rassessment standards\r</span></span></p></li><li data-key=\"241\"><p data-key=\"242\"><span data-key=\"243\"><span data-offset-key=\"243:0\"> Important or tricky teacher moves\r</span></span></p></li><li data-key=\"244\"><p data-key=\"245\"><span data-key=\"246\"><span data-offset-key=\"246:0\"> Experiences/learning activities that your students will enjoy and find motivating\r</span></span></p></li><li data-key=\"247\"><p data-key=\"248\"><span data-key=\"249\"><span data-offset-key=\"249:0\"> Anything that seems like it might be challenging for your students\r</span></span></p></li></ul><div data-key=\"250\" class=\"BlockWrapper__block--U1QBoci undefined\"><div class=\"BlockHeader__component--Pa9vmaO\"><h2><span data-key=\"251\"><span data-offset-key=\"251:0\">Reflect and Share</span></span></h2></div></div><p data-key=\"252\"><span data-key=\"253\"><span data-offset-key=\"253:0\">Now that you have taken some time to choose a text set and to look closely at the lesson sequence, go to the</span><span data-offset-key=\"253:1\"><strong> </strong></span></span><a target=\"_blank\" data-key=\"254\" href=\"/groups/ranking-evidence-secondary-smlc-lesson-study/46a2652f-cfc8-4050-8576-3c29158bbc1c/discussions/preparing-to-teach/06541a77-1492-45f8-ba98-543b26a0d9de\" class=\"Link__component--jdN63pa Link__theme--hyperlink--arKLCP7\"><span data-key=\"255\"><span data-offset-key=\"255:0\"><strong>Preparing to Teach Discussion</strong></span></span></a><span data-key=\"256\"><span data-offset-key=\"256:0\"><strong> </strong></span><span data-offset-key=\"256:1\">to share what you discovered.</span></span></p><div data-key=\"257\" class=\"BlockWrapper__block--U1QBoci undefined\"><div class=\"BlockImage__component--np2T9it\" data-alignment=\"left\"><figure class=\"BlockImage__figure--trN7ey9\"><img class=\"BlockImage__image--Oer5P08\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/com.appolearning.files/production/uploads/uploaded_file/6f12669f-0bcf-4ad8-aeeb-e88a8234765d/Discussion_icon_2022_copy_small.png\"></figure></div></div><p data-key=\"260\"><span data-key=\"261\"><span data-offset-key=\"261:0\"><strong>Reflect on the following:</strong></span></span></p><ul data-key=\"262\"><li data-key=\"263\"><p data-key=\"264\"><span data-key=\"265\"><span data-offset-key=\"265:0\">Which text set did you choose and why?</span></span></p></li><li data-key=\"266\"><p data-key=\"267\"><span data-key=\"268\"><span data-offset-key=\"268:0\">What are you looking forward to in teaching this resource?</span></span></p></li><li data-key=\"269\"><p data-key=\"270\"><span data-key=\"271\"><span data-offset-key=\"271:0\">What might be challenging, for you and/or your students?</span></span></p></li><li data-key=\"272\"><p data-key=\"273\"><span data-key=\"274\"><span data-offset-key=\"274:0\">What adaptations or adjustments do you think you might need to make?</span></span></p></li><li data-key=\"275\"><p data-key=\"276\"><span data-key=\"277\"><span data-offset-key=\"277:0\">Other questions or ideas</span></span></p></li></ul><p data-key=\"278\"><span data-key=\"279\"><span data-offset-key=\"279:0\">Remember, please also reply to each other offering appreciation, asking questions, and adding new ideas that spark discussion.</span></span></p><p data-key=\"280\"><span data-key=\"281\"><span data-offset-key=\"281:0\"><span data-slate-zero-width=\"n\">​</span></span></span></p>"
}